001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations;
002
003import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.Message;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.MessageType;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.UndefinedMessage;
006import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.bluetooth.Characteristic;
007import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.models.KnownApiVersion;
008import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.models.SupportedDevices;
009
010import java.lang.annotation.ElementType;
011import java.lang.annotation.Retention;
012import java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;
013import java.lang.annotation.Target;
014
015@Target(ElementType.TYPE)
016@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
017public @interface MessageProps {
018    byte opCode();
019    int size() default 0;
020    boolean variableSize() default false;
021    boolean stream() default false;
022    boolean signed() default false;
023    MessageType type();
024    Class<? extends Message> response() default UndefinedMessage.class;
025    Class<? extends Message> request() default UndefinedMessage.class;
026    KnownApiVersion minApi() default KnownApiVersion.API_V2_1;
027    SupportedDevices supportedDevices() default SupportedDevices.ALL;
028    Characteristic characteristic() default Characteristic.CURRENT_STATUS;
029    boolean modifiesInsulinDelivery() default false;
030}
